summary: A small collection of random modder\'s resources.
descriptionHtml:
This is a constantly growing collection of resources (Meshes and Scripts) I made. They are mostly leftovers from my first attempts at retexturing, from abandoned mods or ongoing projects. They are of varying quality, heavily depending on my skill and enthusiasm at the time I made them. Feel free to use / improve / redistribute these resources however you like.

Currently included Meshes:[list]
[*] A retexture of the common Ship (interior and exterior), with the Katariah tileset
[*] Upperclass retextures of the Tanning Rack, Forge and a small Crate
[*] An open section of the Dwemer Pipes, complete with (working) hatches
[*] A Dwemer Smelter, fully animated and usable
[*] A bunch of new Editor Markers / Dummy Items
[*] A Morrowind/Ashland-style Wind Chime, complete made from scratch (include a static and a fully havoked version)
[*] Some minor stuff not really worth mentioning here (and I\'m lazy)
[/list]

Currently included Scripts:[list]
[*] ReferencSelector: Shows a Message Box, and enables one of multiple Items, depending on the players choice, disable the others
[/list]
author: Tueffel
